    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This suite offers a single room, equipped with both a key and a code lock, that can house a number of prisoners equal to twice the ship's suite capacity by size, as shown in the Starship Size Suite Capacity table. Slave pen doors are magnetically sealed to prevent them opening in the event of power failure. When a creature completes a long rest involving this suite, their exhaustion level is not reduced. Additionally, for each week spent in this suite, creatures suffer 1 level of exhaustion.</p>",
